<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Joe McGinley</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--fg);
            --bg: #fff;
            --fg: #000;
            transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        }
        
        body.dark {
            --bg: #000;
            --fg: #fff;
        }
        
        a {
            color: var(--fg);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            border: 2px solid var(--fg);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: normal;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        
        .bio {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .bio:last-of-type {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .links a:hover {
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
        }
        
        section {
            border: 2px solid var(--fg);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        
        .section-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .project {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg);
            padding: 12px 0;
        }
        
        .project:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .project-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .project-name a:hover {
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
        }
        
        .project-desc {
            margin-top: 4px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .arch-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
            gap: 2px;
        }
        
        .arch-item {
            display: contents;
        }
        
        .arch-key {
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
            padding: 6px 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .arch-val {
            border: 1px solid var(--fg);
            padding: 6px 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        footer {
            border: 2px solid var(--fg);
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        footer a:hover {
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
        }
        
        .cluster-info {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .arch-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
            }
            .arch-key {
                font-size: 10px;
            }
        }
        
        .toggle-btn {
            background: var(--fg);
            color: var(--bg);
            border: none;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .toggle-btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .header-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="header-row">
                <h1>Joe McGinley</h1>
                <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="document.body.classList.toggle('dark')">[INVERT]</button>
            </div>
            <p class="bio">Mostly I build tools and infrastructure that other engineers don't have to think about.</p>
            <p class="bio">Based in Vancouver, originally from Scotland.</p>
            <p class="bio">Senior Platform Engineer @ Semgrep.</p>
            <div class="links">
                <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#96fcf9f3d6fcf9fbf5f1ffb8f2f3e0">[EMAIL]</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jomcgi/">[LINKEDIN]</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/jomcgi">[GITHUB]</a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section>
            <div class="section-header">Side Quests</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name"><a href="https://trips.jomcgi.dev">trips.jomcgi.dev</a></div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Road trip tracker for our Yukon drive. On-the-road inference to detect wildlife from a car-mounted GoPro.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name"><a href="/frank">Frank x Vancouver</a></div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Trip website for my sister's visit.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name"><a href="https://hikes.jomcgi.dev">hikes.jomcgi.dev</a></div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Find hikes in Scotland with good weather right now. Forecast updates every 30 minutes.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <div class="section-header">Building</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name">Stargazer</div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Map of good stargazing spots. Filters for road access, low light pollution, clear forecasts.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name">Sextant</div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Generates typed Go for Kubernetes operators from declarative state machines.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name">Opencode WebUI</div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Self-hosted coding assistant. Sessions run as pods with access to multiple LLM backends.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="project-name">Cloudflare Operator</div>
                    <div class="project-desc">Annotate a service with a domain → operator creates tunnels, DNS records, zero trust rules.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <div class="section-header">Homelab</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="cluster-info">5-node Kubernetes cluster running in my office</div>
                <div class="arch-grid">
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Monorepo</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">Don't want to spread context or build processes across repos</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Bazel</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">Multi-language builds, multiplatform images with apko. Write a rule once, benefit for years</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">GitOps</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">ArgoCD — mirrors what I maintain at work, scales to multiple clusters</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Ingress</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">Cloudflare Tunnels in-cluster via my operator, zero trust SSO</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Policy</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">Kyverno to catch mistakes — no peer reviews here</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Observability</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">OTel auto-instrumentation where suitable, self-hosted SigNoz</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Storage</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">Longhorn for PVs, avoiding state where possible. Critical data backed up offsite</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="arch-item">
                        <div class="arch-key">Mesh</div>
                        <div class="arch-val">Linkerd for service-to-service mTLS and telemetry</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <a href="https://github.com/jomcgi/homelab">github.com/jomcgi/homelab</a> — public soon